                <h1>"Jesus on the Cross: A Symbol of Faith and Sacrifice"</h1>
                <p>The image of Jesus on the cross is a powerful symbol of sacrifice and redemption in Christianity. It represents the central event of the crucifixion, where Jesus bore the sins of humanity. This poignant depiction speaks to believers, evoking deep emotions of faith, hope, and love. Such images serve as a reminder of His message and the promise of salvation.</p>
